responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "8A6C8207422639714A82519EE301376F", "You must have faith when you enter the Midnight Carnival. Faith in your decisions, faith in your fortitude and faith in the creatures of the night. But most important, faith in the Master Sire, the Destroyer of those evils that lurk in the light. Give yourself to the carnival and give yourself to he who infects the world with unending happiness.")
